Customize your registration page for webinars
As the host, you can customize the attendee registration page for your webinar to provide a more personalized experience. The color theme, logo, background, and speakersâ€™ profile can be customized and previewed to see how it will look on computers and mobile devices.
1
Sign in User Hub, then click Webinars.
2
Select your webinar and in the Branding section, click Edit.
Click Layout to customize your theme, logo, background image, text colors, and buttons.
Click Content to show or hide the host, the speaker, or the agenda.
3
To see what your page looks like in desktop or mobile, click or .
4
Click Save.